*  Global constants:

*   The maximum number of pixels within an area about a bright pixel 
*   that can be used. 
      INTEGER TOP1__PIXN
      PARAMETER ( TOP1__PIXN = 10000 )

*   A very small value that is greater than 0.0. The actual
*   value is not important.
      REAL TOP1__VSMAL
      PARAMETER ( TOP1__VSMAL = 1.E-20 )
